viewed it as three different pillars, more or less, where I think the machine learning and

00:03:29.960 --> 00:03:36.520
modeling and AI is one of those pillars. But I think equally as important is going to be

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:41.320
kind of the actual data science product, whether that's like a dashboard or a report.

