vague general topics. I wonder how Dave is going to talk about them or what he's going to find

00:04:40.359 --> 00:04:45.559
exciting about them. And then when I listened to you talk about them, I was so enthralled. I was

00:04:45.559 --> 00:04:49.880
like, yes, I am in such agreement with all of these things. Let's talk about this forever. Let's

